[img]https://i.imgur.com/6o9HyTD.png[/img]
This is a compatibility patch for Political & Economic Changes and Urban Synergy Unleashed.

[h3]Requires the originals: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3371689443]Urban Synergy Unleashed[/url] and [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=2980730952]Political & Economic Changes[/url].[/h3]

Load order doesn't matter.

[img]https://i.imgur.com/UN80Om5.png[/img]
This patch has been mostly provided by [url=https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561199244678890/myworkshopfiles/?appid=529340]OboySnifferen[/url].

